title: We Finally Take The Corvair Off Road.
author: Matt's Off Road Recovery
description:
So we're building a Corvair rescue truck and we're testing it out in the dunes at Sand Hollow. 

Get Your Matt’s Off Road Recovery Tumbler Cup Today
https://mattsoffroadrecovery.com/collections/accessories/products/tumbler-cup

Subscribe  https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwdVOry0oNF9WIe_3uCfz9Q/?sub_confirmation=1

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S8MRajC1gho&list=PLEi6DFDVEqybxvABm2SDL4iqKO3PHRFVY

Car Thief Destroys GMC Sierra, Extremely Difficult Rescue!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EhxeUGQwqrc&list=PLEi6DFDVEqybxvABm2SDL4iqKO3PHRFVY

The Corvair Hits The Road!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vtIvSUQoDEo&list=PLEi6DFDVEqybxvABm2SDL4iqKO3PHRFVY

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_GiJhbnsQdQ&list=PLEi6DFDVEqybxvABm2SDL4iqKO3PHRFVY

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x250sUg9RAg&list=PLEi6DFDVEqybxvABm2SDL4iqKO3PHRFVY

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r8IfXPm9zrU&list=PLEi6DFDVEqybxvABm2SDL4iqKO3PHRFVY

Follow us on Facebook!

Please like, subscribe, and share! 

Thanks for watching, from all of us at Matt's off-road recovery!
